text: Durbar Rajshahi (formerly Rajshahi Royals) is a professional franchise cricket team that plays in the Bangladesh Premier League (BPL). They were formed in 2012, and represent Rajshahi Division. The team play their home matches at the Shaheed Qamaruzzaman Stadium. ==References== Category:Bangladesh Premier League teams Category:2012 establishments in Bangladesh
